A minimalistic overhead view of a sleek desk surface showing five different devices arranged in a descending spiral pattern by size: a large desktop monitor, a laptop, a tablet, a smartphone, and a tiny smartwatch. Each device displays the same abstract geometric pattern in deep teal and warm orange, but the pattern becomes progressively simplified on smaller screens. The devices cast subtle shadows on a clean white surface with faint grid lines. The composition emphasizes the dramatic scale difference between screens, with the monitor dominating the upper portion while the smartwatch appears almost like a speck in the lower corner. Soft directional lighting from above creates depth without harsh contrasts. No text, logos, or brand identifiers visible on any device.
